   With that though it may take time for a guild, or multiple-guilds(really like that Idea) to step forward. The cycle has come round again with your retirement Kell, Also with Komm's in the Dragon raids. New expierences to be had new lessons to learn for those who take the lead. This can can be extremely fun, frightining and be a large hassle all at the same time. All who accept this role and fulfill it are strong people. <br>
